{"tid":155538,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"45歲前未發達  你可以放棄","createTime":"2017-03-14T06:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T06:47:03.000Z","uid":57695,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f27f99ba4073279d888d2238f8644c898b13e4b","tid":155538,"uid":57695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:22:10.000Z","msg":"45歲前未發達 &nbsp;你可以放棄<br />\n<br />\n好多打工仔，想留前鬥後，晚年發大達？原來睇外國數據同你講，供完樓年齡先發達？No Way。<br />\n<br />\n以下外國一篇觀察文章講⋯<br />\n<br />\n最近美國有項Federal Reserve嘅半世紀研究，針對5百萬名打工仔嘅40年薪金表現，結果顯示，一般打工仔收入嘅爆發期，係25至35歲，又稱黃金十年；過咗45歲，通常都會lifetime收入下降，而喺呢個時期先爆上發達嘅個案，現實上少之又少。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n（圖表：綠色線代表45至55歲，真係唔掂）<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n（圖表：唔同收入水平階層，都係45歲就開始無力。）<br />\n<br />\n照咁睇，20歲基本上已經決定咗你係咪發達，唔係個個都可以中年突圍。<br />\n<br />\n所以，點解「年輕時入錯行就一世捱窮」，呢個謎，今日終於解開了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://centralmarket.tumblr.com/post/158338204035/45%E6%AD%B2%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%AA%E7%99%BC%E9%81%94-%E4%BD%A0%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcentralmarket.tumblr.com%2Fpost%2F158338204035%2F45%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%259C%25AA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E9%2581%2594-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%25A3%2584&d=8Se%2B9W40ah4Gl3auq3G%2BurDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=4c04f8d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://centralmarket.tumblr.com/post/158338204035/45%E6%AD%B2%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%AA%E7%99%BC%E9%81%94-%E4%BD%A0%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84</a>"},{"pid":"3dc736cf6d88b886bf9c0d1c1610d4c6b6c8db24","tid":155538,"uid":57695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:22:43.000Z","msg":"完了吧如無意外"},{"pid":"f558e0ee166362f6ed71dd85a3be7a0d1075b667","tid":155538,"uid":88592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:27:19.000Z","msg":"48歲（破產）"},{"pid":"62b7497bffb528e68c9fcc5019adc09f0953e223","tid":155538,"uid":235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T06:27:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被